26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_msvld_mcp89.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:32 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31#include <nvif/class.h>
32
33static const struct nvkm_falcon_func
34mcp89_msvld = {
35 .pmc_enable = 0x04008000,
36 .init = g98_msvld_init,
37 .sclass = {
38 { -1, -1, IGT21A_MSVLD },
39 {}
40 }
41};
42
43int
44mcp89_msvld_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index,
45 struct nvkm_engine **pengine)
46{
47 return nvkm_msvld_new_(&mcp89_msvld, device, index, pengine);
48}
